title: Plaqueboymax reveals Tyla DMs live on Twitch then deletes Valentine voice note before NBA All Star Weekend
summary_full: Plaqueboymax went viral after revealing he sent and deleted a Valentine voice note to Tyla during a February 12 Twitch stream shared by @FearedBuck on X. In the same livestream, he announced a Bose collaboration for NBA All-Star Weekend, including projects with NBA players and basketball runs with Lil Yachty and the Concrete Boys.
